{# Ventra ingest unhandled failure (code bug / DB outage). Sent to ops. #}
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f5f6fa;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#1f2937;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f5f6fa;padding:24px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:24px 28px;border-bottom:1px solid #fecaca;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b91c1c,#ef4444);color:#ffffff;">
                <div style="font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:0.9;">HHA Ventra ingest · UNHANDLED FAILURE</div>
                <div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px;">Ingest failed — {{ drop_date }}</div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:24px 28px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:14px;color:#4b5563;">
                  The Ventra ingest job exited with an unhandled error — distinct from a validation quarantine. KEDA will retry up to 3 times before dead-lettering the queue message; if all retries fail, the manifest event lands in the vendor-deadletter container for manual triage.
                </p>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin-bottom:14px;border:1px solid #fecaca;border-left:4px solid #ef4444;border-radius:8px;background:#fef2f2;">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:14px 16px;">
                      <div style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#991b1b;font-weight:700;">
                        {{ error_type }}
                      </div>
                      <div style="font-size:14px;color:#374151;margin-top:6px;font-family:monospace;word-break:break-word;">{{ error_message }}</div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin-bottom:14px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;">
                  <tr><td style="padding:4px 0;">Run ID</td><td style="padding:4px 0;font-family:monospace;color:#374151;">{{ run_id }}</td></tr>
                  <tr><td style="padding:4px 0;">Correlation ID</td><td style="padding:4px 0;font-family:monospace;color:#374151;">{{ correlation_id }}</td></tr>
                  <tr><td style="padding:4px 0;">Drop date</td><td style="padding:4px 0;color:#374151;">{{ drop_date }}</td></tr>
                </table>

                <p style="margin:16px 0 8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#1f2937;font-weight:600;">Triage</p>
                <ol style="margin:0 0 0 18px;padding:0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;">
                  <li>App Insights — search by <code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;">correlation_id == "{{ correlation_id }}"</code> for the full stack trace</li>
                  <li>Check <code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;">ops.ingest_run WHERE run_id = '{{ run_id }}'</code> for the recorded error_details JSONB</li>
                  <li>If KEDA retries also fail, examine <code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;">vendor-deadletter/</code> for the orphaned event</li>
                  <li>Runbook: <a href="https://github.com/DandaAkhilReddy/hhadashboard/blob/main/hha-dashboard/docs/04-operations/RUNBOOK.md#ventra-failure" style="color:#4338ca;">docs/04-operations/RUNBOOK.md#ventra-failure</a></li>
                </ol>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:18px 28px;border-top:1px solid #fecaca;background:#fafafa;font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;">
                Sent automatically by the Ventra ingest job. Inbound files persist; replay after fix.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
